-XXX/` with a consistent 4-file structure:\n- `proposal.md` -- Overview, purpose, scope, impact analysis, alternatives, acceptance criteria\n- `design.md` -- Architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, test strategy\n- `delta-spec.md` -- Gherkin-style requirements\n- `tasks.md` -- Implementation task清单\n\n| AR | Title | Module | Status |\n|----|-------|--------|--------|\n| AR-001 | CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 | `pkg/apis` | Template with TODOs filled |\n| AR-002 | CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 | `pkg/apis` | Template with TODOs filled |\n| AR-003 | CRD 共享类型与常量 | `pkg/apis` | Template with TODOs filled |\n| AR-004 | WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 | `pkg/workloadmanager` | Template with TODOs filled |\n| **AR-005** | **Sandbox 创建处理器** | **`pkg/workloadmanager`** | **Skeleton with all TODOs** |\n\n**AR-005 current state** (all files are skeleton/TODO):\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md` -- 35 lines, all sections are `<!-- TODO -->`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/design.md` -- 29 lines, all sections are `<!-- TODO -->`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md` -- 9 lines, all sections are `<!-- TODO -->`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/tasks.md` -- 10 lines, `<!-- TODO -->`\n\n---\n\n### 4. AR (Architecture Request) Document Pattern\n\nThe established pattern from AR-001 through AR-004 shows:\n\n**proposal.md sections:**\n1. 概述 (Overview)\n2. 元信息 (Module, Language, Size)\n3. 目的 (Purpose)\n4. 范围 -- 包含 / 不包含 (In/Out of scope)\n5. 影响分析 -- 直接影响 / 下游依赖 / 无影响的组件 (Impact analysis)\n6. 备选方案 (Alternatives considered, with rationale)\n7. 验收标准 (Acceptance criteria)\n8. 状态 (Status checkboxes)\n\n**design.md sections:**\n1. 架构 (Architecture)\n2. 数据结构 (Data structures)\n3. API 契约 (API contracts)\n4. 错误处理 (Error handling)\n5. 测试策略 (Test strategy)\n6. 实现步骤 (Implementation steps)\n7. 风险与缓解 (Risks & mitigations)\n\n**delta-spec.md sections:**\n1. Purpose\n2. Requirements (Gherkin format: GIVEN/WHEN/THEN)\n\n---\n\n### 5. Sandbox-Related Code and Docs\n\n**Key sandbox-related files:**\n\n| File | Content |\n|------|---------|\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | **475 lines** -- Extremely detailed design covering the entire sandbox lifecycle: CRD types, K8sClient, SandboxReconciler, garbage collector, token cache, build logic, CLI flags, store interface |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` | **176 lines** -- Gherkin-style requirements for sandbox creation, deletion, GC, auth, pod IP resolution |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md` | **271 lines** -- Helm chart, Dockerfiles, RBAC, Makefile targets, CRD definitions |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md` | **96 lines** -- Deployment requirements |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` | **227 lines** -- AR-004 delta spec with detailed Gherkin requirements for HTTP server, CRUD APIs, health checks, informer integration |\n| `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` | **40 lines** -- TDD requirements including `CreateSandbox` and `DeleteSession` tests |\n\n**Critical types from `pkg/common/types` (documented in sandbox-orchestration/design.md):**\n- `SandboxInfo` -- sandbox metadata (Kind, SandboxID, Namespace, Name, EntryPoints, SessionID, CreatedAt, ExpiresAt, Status)\n- `SandboxEntryPoint` -- (Path, Protocol, Endpoint)\n- `CreateSandboxRequest` -- (Kind, Name, Namespace) with `Validate()` method\n- `CreateSandboxResponse` -- (SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints)\n\n**GVR variables (from sandbox-orchestration/design.md):**\n- `AgentRuntimeGVR` -- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes`\n- `CodeInterpreterGVR` -- `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/codeinterpreters`\n- `SandboxGVR` -- `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes`\n- `SandboxClaimGVR` -- `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims`\n\n**Key constants:**\n- `SessionIdLabelKey` = `\"runtime.agentcube.io/session-id\"`\n- `WorkloadNameLabelKey` = `\"runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name\"`\n- `SandboxNameLabelKey` = `\"runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name\"`\n- `DefaultSandboxTTL` = 8 hours\n- `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` = 15 minutes\n\n---\n\n### 6. go.mod -- Dependencies\n\n**Path:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod`\n\n```\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\ngo 1.25.0\n\nDirect dependencies:\n  github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1\n  k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n  k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1\n  k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1\n  sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2\n```\n\nNote: The sandbox-orchestration/design.md references additional dependencies that appear in the full go.mod (Gin, go-redis, valkey-go, golang-jwt, uuid, gomonkey, miniredis, agent-sandbox) -- the current go.mod shown is a trimmed version.\n\n---\n\n### 7. deployment/ and spec/ Directories\n\n**deployment/ directory:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/design.md` -- Comprehensive Helm chart design, Dockerfiles, RBAC rules, CRD definitions, Makefile targets\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/spec.md` -- Deployment requirements in Gherkin format\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/deployment/client-go.md` -- Generated client-go library documentation (referenced in `.sdd_prompt.md`)\n\n**Spec files are distributed per-component** (not in a single `spec/` directory):\n- `sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`\n- `deployment/spec.md`\n- `session-routing/spec.md`\n- `session-store/spec.md`\n- `code-execution/spec.md`\n- `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n- `ci-cd/spec.md`\n- `idle-cleanup/spec.md`\n- `python-sdk/spec.md`\n- `integrations/spec.md`\n- `test_spec.md` (root level)\n- `delta-spec.md` (root level, AR-004)\n\n---\n\n### 8. Key Insights for Writing AR-005 Proposal\n\n**What AR-005 should cover (based on context):**\n\n1. **Sandbox creation handler** for both `POST /v1/agent-runtime` and `POST /v1/code-interpreter` endpoints\n2. **Request validation** using `CreateSandboxRequest.Validate()`\n3. **Kubernetes resource creation** -- creating `Sandbox` or `SandboxClaim` CRs via the typed client or dynamic client\n4. **Watcher registration** -- one-shot watcher for sandbox status \"running\" (up to 2 min timeout)\n5. **Store placeholder** -- `StoreSandbox` before CR creation, `UpdateSandbox` after pod IP resolution\n6. **Pod IP resolution** -- prefer sandbox name, fallback to annotation `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name`, then label selector\n7. **Response building** -- `CreateSandboxResponse` with SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n8. **Error handling** -- 400 for validation, 404 for missing templates, 401 for auth errors, 500 for internal/timeout\n9. **Rollback** -- delete created CR on failure (30s timeout context)\n10. **Warm pool support** -- for CodeInterpreter with `WarmPoolSize > 0`, create SandboxClaim instead of full Sandbox\n11. **Auth mode handling** -- inject `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` when `AuthMode == picod`\n\n**Existing code to leverage:**\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/response/response.go` -- `Created()`, `Error()`, `ErrorWithID()` helpers\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` -- All CRD types, shared types, constants\n- `client-go/` -- Generated typed clients, informers, listers\n- The detailed sandbox creation logic documented in `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` (lines 271-475)\n\n**Files to create/modify for AR-005 implementation:**\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go` (new)\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create_test.go` (new)\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/agent_runtime.go` (new or modify)\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/code_interpreter.go` (new or modify)\n- `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/` files (as needed)\n- `changes/AR-005/proposal.md` (fill in TODOs)\n- `changes/AR-005/design.md` (fill in TODOs)\n- `changes/AR-005/delta-spec.md` (fill in TODOs)\n- `changes/AR-005/tasks.md` (fill in TODOs)\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28926b3d6ffebrrWAlmqmnYwrQ","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775815445542,"end":1775815579101}}}}
