{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775815583449,"sessionID":"ses_28926e5e7ffez1hwseVg6EjPpj","part":{"id":"prt_d76db6352001ffSZo1VLJkfL1G","messageID":"msg_d76db562d001CXMVROba4RmLm1","sessionID":"ses_28926e5e7ffez1hwseVg6EjPpj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_b39e07e5c0bd4b6ab204709f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: <!-- TODO: 填写概述 -->\n6: \n7: ## 元信息\n8: \n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n10: - **Language**: Go\n11: - **Size**: M\n12: \n13: ## 目的\n14: \n15: <!-- TODO: 填写目的 -->\n16: \n17: ## 范围\n18: \n19: ### 包含\n20: \n21: <!-- TODO: 填写包含范围 -->\n22: \n23: ### 不包含\n24: \n25: <!-- TODO: 填写不包含范围 -->\n26: \n27: ## 验收标准\n28: \n29: <!-- TODO: 填写验收标准 -->\n30: \n31: ## 状态\n32: \n33: - [ ] 提案审查\n34: - [ ] 实现\n35: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 35 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-005: Sandbox 创建处理器\n\n## 概述\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写概述 -->\n\n## 元信息\n\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n\n## 目的\n\n<!-- TODO: 填写目的 -->\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-005/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775815583441,"end":1775815583447}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775815584716,"sessionID":"ses_28926e5e7ffez1hwseVg6EjPpj","part":{"id":"prt_d76db6772001GxkX6hzdrnlXDs","messageID":"msg_d76db562d001CXMVROba4RmLm1","sessionID":"ses_28926e5e7ffez1hwseVg6EjPpj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5e2970aa4f5f47a29459160a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块建立 HTTP 服务框架，提供 WorkloadManager 的 RESTful API 接口层，作为 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心控制面入口。\n6: \n7: ## 元信息\n8: \n9: - **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n10: - **Language**: Go\n11: - **Size**: M\n12: \n13: ## 目的\n14: \n15: WorkloadManager 是 AgentCube 的核心控制面组件，负责通过 Kubernetes API 管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 资源的生命周期（创建、查询、更新、删除沙箱会话）。本变更将建立完整的 HTTP 服务框架，使 Router、CLI 和 SDK 等下游消费者能够通过标准化的 RESTful API 与 WorkloadManager 交互，实现沙箱的创建、查询、销毁和状态管理。\n16: \n17: 具体目标：\n18: 1. 提供统一的 HTTP 服务启动/停止生命周期管理\n19: 2. 暴露 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 CRUD 端点\n20: 3. 提供健康检查端点供 Kubernetes 探针使用\n21: 4. 建立请求日志、恢复和验证中间件基础设施\n22: 5. 为 AR-005+ 的会话管理、沙箱调度等高级功能提供可扩展的 HTTP 基座\n23: \n24: ## 范围\n25: \n26: ### 包含\n27: \n28: 1. **HTTP 框架选型与集成** — 引入 `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` 作为 HTTP 框架，与项目现有 Go 1.24.4 工具链和 k8s.io 依赖兼容\n29: 2. **服务结构体** — `Server` struct 封装 `*gin.Engine`、`*http.Server`、配置和 Kubernetes clientset\n30: 3. **路由注册** — 按 RESTful 约定注册以下端点：\n31:    | Method | Path | 说明 |\n32:    |--------|------|------|\n33:    | GET | `/health` | 健康检查（liveness + readiness 共用） |\n34:    | POST | `/v1/agent-runtime` | 创建 AgentRuntime 沙箱 |\n35:    | GET | `/v1/agent-runtime/:name` | 查询 AgentRuntime |\n36:    | PUT | `/v1/agent-runtime/:name` | 更新 AgentRuntime |\n37:    | DELETE | `/v1/agent-runtime/:name` | 删除 AgentRuntime |\n38:    | POST | `/v1/code-interpreter` | 创建 CodeInterpreter 沙箱 |\n39:    | GET | `/v1/code-interpreter/:name` | 查询 CodeInterpreter |\n40:    | PUT | `/v1/code-interpreter/:name` | 更新 CodeInterpreter |\n41:    | DELETE | `/v1/code-interpreter/:name` | 删除 CodeInterpreter |\n42: 4. **Handler 层** — 每个端点对应的 handler 函数，通过 AR-003 定义的共享类型和 AR-001/AR-002 的 CRD 类型与 Kubernetes API 交互\n43: 5. **中间件** — `gin.Logger`（请求日志）、`gin.Recovery`（panic 恢复）、请求 ID 追踪\n44: 6. **配置结构体** — `Config` struct（Port、DebugMode、KubeConfig 路径等）\n45: 7. **优雅关闭** — 通过 `context.Context` 和 `http.Server.Shutdown()` 实现优雅停机\n46: 8. **错误响应统一格式** — 标准 JSON 错误体 `{\"error\": \"message\", \"code\": int}`\n47: 9. **单元测试** — Handler 层使用 fake clientset 进行隔离测试\n48: \n49: ### 不包含\n50: \n51: - Kubernetes Informer/Controller 模式的重调和逻辑（后续变更）\n52: - 沙箱会话的 Redis 状态管理（由 Router + Session Store 负责）\n53: - JWT 认证和鉴权（Router 层负责，WorkloadManager 通过 in-cluster ServiceAccount 信任）\n54: - CodeInterpreter 代码执行引擎（PicoD 职责）\n55: - Helm Chart 部署配置（已有 deployment spec 覆盖）\n56: - E2E 测试（独立变更项）\n57: \n58: ## 服务结构概要\n59: \n60: ```\n61: pkg/workloadmanager/\n62: ├── server.go              # Server struct, NewServer(), Run(), Shutdown()\n63: ├── config.go              # Config struct, 默认值, 环境变量读取\n64: ├── routes.go              # 路由注册, SetupRoutes(engine *gin.Engine)\n65: ├── handler/\n66: │   ├── health.go          # GET /health handler\n67: │   ├── agent_runtime.go   # AgentRuntime CRUD handlers\n68: │   └── code_interpreter.go # CodeInterpreter CRUD handlers\n69: ├── middleware/\n70: │   ├── logger.go          # 请求日志中间件（可选，复用 gin.Logger）\n71: │   └── recovery.go        # Panic 恢复中间件（可选，复用 gin.Recovery）\n72: ├── response/\n73: │   └── response.go        # 统一 JSON 响应格式 helper\n74: ├── server_test.go         # Server 生命周期测试\n75: ├── handler/\n76: │   ├── health_test.go     # 健康检查 handler 测试\n77: │   ├── agent_runtime_test.go  # AgentRuntime handler 测试\n78: │   └── code_interpreter_test.go # CodeInterpreter handler 测试\n79: └── response/\n80:     └── response_test.go   # 响应格式 helper 测试\n81: ```\n82: \n83: ### Server struct\n84: \n85: ```go\n86: type Server struct {\n87:     config    *Config\n88:     engine    *gin.Engine\n89:     httpSrv   *http.Server\n90:     clientset clientset.Interface  // AR-004 生成的 client-go\n91: }\n92: ```\n93: \n94: ### Config struct\n95: \n96: ```go\n97: type Config struct {\n98:     Port         int    // 默认 8080\n99:     KubeConfig   string // 默认空（in-cluster config）\n100:     Debug        bool   // 默认 false\n101: }\n102: ```\n103: \n104: ### 健康响应格式\n105: \n106: - 正常: `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n107: - 异常: `{\"status\": \"error\", \"error\": \"reason\"}`\n108: \n109: ## 影响分析\n110: \n111: ### 直接影响\n112: \n113: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n114: |------|------|------|\n115: | `pkg/workloadmanager/` | 新增 | 完整的 HTTP 服务框架目录和文件 |\n116: | `go.mod` | 新增依赖 | 需添加 `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` |\n117: | `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` | 新增或修改 | 服务启动入口，调用 `pkg/workloadmanager.NewServer()` 和 `Run()` |\n118: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/` | 新增 | CRUD handler 实现，依赖 `client-go` 生成的 typed client |\n119: | `pkg/workloadmanager/response/` | 新增 | 统一响应格式 helper |\n120: \n121: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n122: \n123: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n124: |------|----------|\n125: | Router（session-routing） | 通过 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 调用本变更暴露的 `/v1/agent-runtime` 和 `/v1/code-interpreter` 端点 |\n126: | CLI 工具 | 通过 HTTP API 直接管理沙箱生命周期 |\n127: | Python SDK | 封装本变更的 HTTP 端点为用户提供 Python 接口 |\n128: | E2E 测试 | 验证沙箱创建、查询、删除的完整流程 |\n129: \n130: ### 无影响的组件\n131: \n132: - `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` — API 类型定义已完成（AR-001/AR-002/AR-003），本变更仅消费\n133: - `client-go/` — 已生成的 typed client 代码不受影响，本变更是其消费者\n134: - Session Store（Redis/Valkey）— 存储层独立，WorkloadManager 不直接操作 Redis\n135: - Agentd（idle cleanup）— 通过 store 接口交互，不依赖 WorkloadManager HTTP API\n136: - PicoD（code execution）— 沙箱内组件，与控制面 HTTP 框架无关\n137: - Helm Chart — 部署配置已存在，本变更不改变服务暴露方式（仍为 port 8080 + `/health`）\n138: \n139: ## 备选方案\n140: \n141: ### 方案 A：Gin 框架（已选）\n142: \n143: **优点**：Router 组件（session-routing）已选用 Gin 作为 HTTP 框架，保持技术栈统一；Gin 生态成熟、社区活跃、中间件丰富；性能优秀（基于 httprouter）；与 Go 1.24.4 兼容良好；学习成本低，团队熟悉度高。\n144: **缺点**：引入额外的第三方依赖；Gin v1 已停止大版本更新（但维护稳定）。\n145: \n146: ### 方案 B：标准库 `net/http` + `http.ServeMux`\n147: \n148: **优点**：零额外依赖；Go 1.22+ 的 `ServeMux` 支持方法匹配和路径参数，功能已较完善；长期维护有保障。\n149: **缺点**：缺少内置的中间件链、请求绑定、JSON 验证等便利功能；需要自行实现 panic recovery 和结构化日志；与 Router 组件的技术栈不一致，增加维护认知负担。**否决**。\n150: \n151: ### 方案 C：Echo 框架\n152: \n153: **优点**：API 设计优雅；内置数据绑定和验证；中间件生态丰富。\n154: **缺点**：与 Router 组件的 Gin 技术栈不一致；引入第二个 HTTP 框架增加依赖管理复杂度；团队对 Gin 更熟悉。**否决**。\n155: \n156: ### 方案 D：chi 路由器\n157: \n158: **优点**：轻量级、符合 stdlib 风格；中间件通过独立包提供；与 `net/http` 完全兼容。\n159: **缺点**：缺少内置的 JSON 绑定和验证；需要组合多个包才能达到 Gin 的开箱即用体验；与 Router 组件技术栈不一致。**否决**。\n160: \n161: ### 方案 E：controller-runtime 的 `webhook.Server` / `manager` 模式\n162: \n163: **优点**：与 Kubernetes 控制器生态深度集成；内置 leader election、health probes、metrics。\n164: **缺点**：本变更仅需 HTTP API 服务，不需要完整的控制器运行时；controller-runtime 的 manager 模式过于重量级（M 规模的变更引入过大依赖面）；Router 组件不使用此模式，技术栈分裂。**否决**（可在后续需要 Reconciler 时另行引入）。\n165: \n166: ## 验收标准\n167: \n168: 1. `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` 编译通过\n169: 2. `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` 全部通过\n170: 3. `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` 已添加到 `go.mod` 且 `go mod tidy` 无冲突\n171: 4. 服务启动后监听配置的端口（默认 8080）\n172: 5. `GET /health` 返回 `200 OK` 且响应体为 `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n173: 6. `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 接收合法 AgentRuntime 定义，通过 fake clientset 返回 `200 OK` 及资源信息\n174: 7. `POST /v1/agent-runtime` 接收缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，返回 `400 Bad Request`\n175: 8. `POST /v1/code-interpreter` 接收合法 CodeInterpreter 定义，通过 fake clientset 返回 `200 OK`\n176: 9. 相同 `name` 的连续创建请求行为符合 Kubernetes CRD 语义（Update 或 Conflict）\n177: 10. 服务支持优雅关闭：收到 SIGTERM/SIGINT 后完成现有请求再退出\n178: 11. Gin 模式在 `Config.Debug=false` 时为 `ReleaseMode`，`true` 时为 `DebugMode`\n179: 12. 所有 handler 使用统一的 JSON 错误响应格式 `{\"error\": \"message\"}`\n180: \n181: ## 状态\n182: \n183: - [ ] 提案审查\n184: - [ ] 实现\n185: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 185 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004: WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## 概述\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块建立 HTTP 服务框架，提供 WorkloadManager 的 RESTful API 接口层，作为 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心控制面入口。\n\n## 元信息\n\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n\n## 目的\n\nWorkloadManager 是 AgentCube 的核心控制面组件，负责通过 Kubernetes API 管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 资源的生命周期（创建、查询、更新、删除沙箱会话）。本变更将建立完整的 HTTP 服务框架，使 Router、CLI 和 SDK 等下游消费者能够通过标准化的 RESTful API 与 WorkloadManager 交互，实现沙箱的创建、查询、销毁和状态管理。\n\n具体目标：\n1. 提供统一的 HTTP 服务启动/停止生命周期管理\n2. 暴露 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 CRUD 端点\n3. 提供健康检查端点供 Kubernetes 探针使用","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775815584708,"end":1775815584714}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775815586533,"sessionID":"ses_28926e5e7ffez1hwseVg6EjPpj","part":{"id":"prt_d76db6c51001yOi0ypBz50tla3","messageID":"msg_d76db562d001CXMVROba4RmLm1","sessionID":"ses_28926e5e7ffez1hwseVg6EjPpj","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_c470b8370cc9419a91f5fab6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md","offset":271,"limit":205},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n271: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n272: \n273: ### Config and Server\n274: \n275: ```go\n276: type Config struct {\n277:     Port             string\n278:     RuntimeClassName string\n279:     EnableTLS        bool\n280:     TLSCert          string\n281:     TLSKey           string\n282:     EnableAuth       bool\n283: }\n284: \n285: type Server struct {\n286:     config            *Config\n287:     router            *gin.Engine\n288:     httpServer        *http.Server\n289:     k8sClient         *K8sClient\n290:     sandboxController *SandboxReconciler\n291:     tokenCache        *TokenCache\n292:     informers         *Informers\n293:     storeClient       store.Store\n294:     wg                sync.WaitGroup\n295: }\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ### HTTP routes\n299: \n300: | Method | Path | Auth middleware | Handler |\n301: |--------|------|-----------------|---------|\n302: | GET | `/health` | No | `handleHealth` |\n303: | POST | `/v1/agent-runtime` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleAgentRuntimeCreate` |\n304: | DELETE | `/v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleDeleteSandbox` |\n305: | POST | `/v1/code-interpreter` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleCodeInterpreterCreate` |\n306: | DELETE | `/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` | If `EnableAuth` | `handleDeleteSandbox` |\n307: \n308: ### ErrorResponse\n309: \n310: ```go\n311: type ErrorResponse struct {\n312:     Message string `json:\"message\"`\n313: }\n314: ```\n315: \n316: ### K8sClient and defaults\n317: \n318: ```go\n319: const (\n320:     DefaultSandboxTTL         = 8 * time.Hour\n321:     DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n322: )\n323: \n324: var (\n325:     SessionIdLabelKey         = \"runtime.agentcube.io/session-id\"\n326:     WorkloadNameLabelKey      = \"runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name\"\n327:     SandboxNameLabelKey       = \"runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name\"\n328:     LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"\n329:     IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey  = \"runtime.agentcube.io/idle-timeout\"\n330: )\n331: \n332: type K8sClient struct {\n333:     clientset       *kubernetes.Clientset\n334:     dynamicClient   dynamic.Interface\n335:     scheme          *runtime.Scheme\n336:     baseConfig      *rest.Config\n337:     clientCache     *ClientCache\n338:     dynamicInformer dynamicinformer.DynamicSharedInformerFactory\n339:     informerFactory informers.SharedInformerFactory\n340:     podInformer     cache.SharedIndexInformer\n341:     podLister       listersv1.PodLister\n342: }\n343: ```\n344: \n345: - REST config: `QPS = 50`, `Burst = 100`; in-cluster config else kubeconfig loading rules.\n346: - `NewClientCache(100)` for user dynamic clients.\n347: \n348: ### GVR variables (`informers.go`)\n349: \n350: ```go\n351: var (\n352:     AgentRuntimeGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n353:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\",\n354:     }\n355:     CodeInterpreterGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n356:         Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"codeinterpreters\",\n357:     }\n358:     SandboxGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n359:         Group: \"agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"sandboxes\",\n360:     }\n361:     SandboxClaimGVR = schema.GroupVersionResource{\n362:         Group: \"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"sandboxclaims\",\n363:     }\n364: )\n365: ```\n366: \n367: ### Identity secret (workload_builder.go)\n368: \n369: ```go\n370: const (\n371:     IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n372:     PublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n373: )\n374: \n375: var IdentitySecretNamespace = \"default\" // overridden by env AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE if set\n376: ```\n377: \n378: ### Sandbox reconciler\n379: \n380: ```go\n381: type SandboxReconciler struct {\n382:     client.Client\n383:     Scheme *runtime.Scheme\n384:     watchers map[types.NamespacedName]chan SandboxStatusUpdate\n385:     mu       sync.RWMutex\n386: }\n387: \n388: type SandboxStatusUpdate struct {\n389:     Sandbox *sandboxv1alpha1.Sandbox\n390: }\n391: ```\n392: \n393: - `Reconcile`: when `getSandboxStatus(sandbox) == \"running\"`, notify waiter channel (buffer 1), non-blocking send with `default` branch warning on full channel.\n394: - `getSandboxStatus`: returns `\"running\"` if a condition has `Type == string(sandboxv1alpha1.SandboxConditionReady)` and `Status == metav1.ConditionTrue`, else `\"unknown\"`.\n395: \n396: ### Garbage collector\n397: \n398: ```go\n399: const gcOnceTimeout = 2 * time.Minute\n400: \n401: type garbageCollector struct {\n402:     k8sClient   *K8sClient\n403:     interval    time.Duration\n404:     storeClient store.Store\n405: }\n406: ```\n407: \n408: - `newGarbageCollector(k8s, store, 15*time.Second)` — **GC interval: 15s**.\n409: - Per tick: `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, time.Now().Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout), 16)` — **batch size 16**.\n410: - `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Now(), 16)` — **batch size 16**.\n411: - Single tick context timeout: **2 minutes**.\n412: \n413: ### Token cache\n414: \n415: - `NewTokenCache(1000, 5*time.Minute)` — max entries **1000**, TTL **5m** per entry (LRU + last-access expiry).\n416: \n417: ### Auth context keys\n418: \n419: ```go\n420: type contextKey string\n421: \n422: const (\n423:     contextKeyUserToken          contextKey = \"userToken\"\n424:     contextKeyServiceAccount     contextKey = \"serviceAccount\"\n425:     contextKeyServiceAccountName contextKey = \"serviceAccountName\"\n426:     contextKeyNamespace          contextKey = \"namespace\"\n427: )\n428: ```\n429: \n430: ### CLI flags (`cmd/workload-manager/main.go`)\n431: \n432: | Flag | Default | Meaning |\n433: |------|---------|---------|\n434: | `-port` | `8080` | API port |\n435: | `-runtime-class-name` | `kuasar-vmm` | Stored on `Config.RuntimeClassName` (flag parsed in `main`; **not read** elsewhere in `pkg/workloadmanager` in current source) |\n436: | `-enable-tls` | `false` | TLS |\n437: | `-tls-cert` | `\"\"` | Cert path |\n438: | `-tls-key` | `\"\"` | Key path |\n439: | `-enable-auth` | `false` | TokenReview auth |\n440: \n441: - Controller-runtime manager: metrics bind `0`, health probe `0`.\n442: - Shutdown: HTTP shutdown timeout **15s**, then cancel ctx, `WaitForBackgroundWorkers`, `CloseStore`.\n443: \n444: ### Store dependency\n445: \n446: ```go\n447: // github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store\n448: type Store interface {\n449:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n450:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n451:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n452:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n453:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n454:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n455:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n456:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n457:     Close() error\n458: }\n459: ```\n460: \n461: Server uses `store.Storage()` singleton.\n462: \n463: ### Sandbox build notes\n464: \n465: - AgentRuntime: sandbox name `{workloadName}-{RandString(8)}`, UUID session ID, ports from `spec.Ports`, TTL/idle from `MaxSessionDuration` / `SessionTimeout` when non-nil.\n466: - CodeInterpreter: default ports if empty: single `TargetPort{Port:8080, Protocol:ProtocolTypeHTTP, PathPrefix:\"/\"}`; if `WarmPoolSize > 0`: creates `SandboxClaim` + minimal `Sandbox` metadata only, `sandboxEntry.Kind = SandboxClaimsKind`; else builds full `Sandbox` with container `code-interpreter` and optional `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` when `AuthMode == picod`.\n467: - `buildSandboxObject`: APIVersion `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`, Kind `Sandbox`, labels include `managed-by: agentcube-workload-manager`, annotation `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey` = idle duration string, lifecycle `ShutdownTime` = now+TTL, `Replicas: ptr.To[int32](1)`.\n468: \n469: ### Pod name annotation\n470: \n471: - Read from created sandbox: key from `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox/controllers`.`SandboxPodNameAnnotation` (comment in source documents value `agents.x-k8s.io/sandbox-pod-name`).\n472: \n473: ## CodeInterpreter controller (supplementary)\n474: \n475: - Reconciles `CodeInterpreter`; when `WarmPoolSize > 0` ensures `SandboxTemplate` (name = CI name) and `SandboxWarmPool` (name = CI name, replicas = WarmPoolSize, templateRef name = CI name); injects `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` in template unless `AuthModeNone`; requeues 5s if public key not cached and auth not none.\n\n(End of file - total 475 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager`\n\n### Config and Server\n\n```go\ntype Config struct {\n    Port             string\n    RuntimeClassName string\n    EnableTLS        bool\n    TLSCert          string\n    TLSKey           string\n    EnableAuth       bool\n}\n\ntype Server struct {\n    config            *Config\n    router            *gin.Engine\n    httpServer        *http.Server\n    k8sClient         *K8sClient\n    sandboxController *SandboxReconciler","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/sandbox-orchestration/design.md","time":{"start":1775815586525,"end":1775815586531}}}}
